   Unsupported Browser Need to Register
   You must be using Internet Explorer 4 or Netscape 4 or better to login
   this site. You can still browse the information available here and
   download blank forms, but you cannot access any data until you upgrade
   your browser. These browsers can be downloaded from these links:

      Click to Download Internet Explorer   Click to Download Netscape
                                  Navigator

   Your browser reports itself as (MultiText/0.1) which is not known to be
   a Netscape 4+ or Internet Explorer 4+ browser. If you feel you have
   received this page in error, please Contact Us. If you are not
   registered as an Employer with EDD, find out how.
